com.dukes.klein.parser.node

Class OperatorNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dukes.lang.parser.node.AbstractSyntaxNode
      • com.dukes.lang.parser.node.ExpressionNode
        • com.dukes.klein.parser.node.OperatorNode

  • public class OperatorNode
extends ExpressionNode
    This class describes an operation in Klein. This can be either a binary or unary operation. If the left side is a NullNode, then the expression is a unary operation; otherwise, it is a binary expression. No null values should be added to the operator node. The operation should be a valid Klein operation; however, this is not checked within this class.
    Since:
    0.3.0
